<mxfile>
  <diagram name="4レイヤーアーキテクチャ" id="page-1">
    <mxGraphModel dx="900" dy="620" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1400" pageHeight="960" math="0" shadow="0" background="#FFFFFF">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <!-- 白背景矩形（必須） -->
        <mxCell id="bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="0" width="1400" height="960" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <!-- タイトル -->
        <mxCell id="title" value="ソフトウェアレイヤー構成（3 アプリ＋2 バックエンドバイナリ）" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="250" y="16" width="900" height="34" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== プレゼンテーション層（フロントエンド 3 アプリ） ===== -->
        <!-- layer_fe_bg: x=80, y=60, w=1240, h=160 → bbox y=60..220 -->
        <mxCell id="layer_fe_bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="60" width="1240" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="layer_fe_label" value="プレゼンテーション層" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="96" y="68" width="220" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-HA: x=110, y=90, w=240, h=110 → right edge x=350, bottom y=200 -->
        <mxCell id="fe_ha" value="&lt;b&gt;ハンディ APP&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;(FE-HA)&lt;br&gt;React Native / TypeScript&lt;br&gt;SQLite + SQLCipher" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="110" y="90" width="240" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-MA: x=580, y=90, w=240, h=110 -->
        <mxCell id="fe_ma" value="&lt;b&gt;マスタメンテ APP&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;(FE-MA)&lt;br&gt;React + TypeScript (Vite)&lt;br&gt;SOP 編集・承認・公開" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="580" y="90" width="240" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-MC: x=970, y=90, w=240, h=110 → right edge x=1210 -->
        <mxCell id="fe_mc" value="&lt;b&gt;管理コンソール&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;(FE-MC)&lt;br&gt;React + TypeScript (Vite)&lt;br&gt;監査・ユーザー管理・帳票" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="970" y="90" width="240" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== バックエンド層（2 バイナリ） ===== -->
        <!-- layer_be_bg: x=80, y=270, w=1240, h=160 → bbox y=270..430 -->
        <mxCell id="layer_be_bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="270" width="1240" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="layer_be_label" value="バックエンド層（2 バイナリ）" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="96" y="278" width="280" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- be_terminal: x=110, y=300, w=500, h=110 → top y=300, bottom y=410, left x=110 -->
        <mxCell id="be_terminal" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_terminal_api&lt;/b&gt;  (MOD-BE-001)  ポート: 8080&lt;br&gt;Rust + axum + tokio&lt;br&gt;Idempotency / レート制限 / 作業ログ受信 / Outbox Consumer&lt;br&gt;DB ロール: app_event_insert + app_read" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="110" y="300" width="500" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- be_master: x=710, y=300, w=500, h=110 → right edge x=1210, bottom y=410 -->
        <mxCell id="be_master" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_master_api&lt;/b&gt;  (MOD-BE-010)  ポート: 8081&lt;br&gt;Rust + axum + tokio&lt;br&gt;SOP 編集 / 承認 / 監査 / ユーザー管理 / HashChainVerifier&lt;br&gt;DB ロール: app_write + app_read" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="710" y="300" width="500" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== 共有クレート層 ===== -->
        <!-- layer_crate_bg: x=80, y=480, w=1240, h=140 → bbox y=480..620 -->
        <mxCell id="layer_crate_bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="480" width="1240" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="layer_crate_label" value="共有クレート層（両バイナリが依存）" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="96" y="488" width="310" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_domain: x=100, y=510, w=170, h=90 → center x=185 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_domain" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_domain&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-002&lt;br&gt;ドメインモデル/Service/Trait" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="100" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_db: x=290, y=510, w=170, h=90 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_db" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_db&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-004&lt;br&gt;sqlx クエリ/プール" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="290" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_auth: x=480, y=510, w=170, h=90 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_auth" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_auth&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-005&lt;br&gt;JWT RS256 / RBAC" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="480" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_hash: x=670, y=510, w=170, h=90 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_hash" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_hash_chain&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-003&lt;br&gt;SHA-256 チェーン検証" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="670" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_outbox: x=860, y=510, w=170, h=90 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_outbox" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_outbox&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-006&lt;br&gt;Outbox Consumer (tokio)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="860" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- crate_webhook: x=1050, y=510, w=170, h=90 -->
        <mxCell id="crate_webhook" value="&lt;b&gt;wnav_webhook&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;MOD-BE-007&lt;br&gt;Webhook / HMAC 署名" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1050" y="510" width="170" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== インフラ層 ===== -->
        <!-- layer_infra_bg: x=80, y=670, w=1240, h=140 → bbox y=670..810 -->
        <mxCell id="layer_infra_bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="670" width="1240" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="layer_infra_label" value="インフラ層" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="96" y="678" width="160" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- infra_pg: x=200, y=690, w=320, h=100 → bbox x=200..520, y=690..790. center_x=360, center_y=740 -->
        <mxCell id="infra_pg" value="&lt;b&gt;PostgreSQL 16+&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;DBロール3分離&lt;br&gt;app_event_insert / app_write / app_read" style="shape=cylinder3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;boundedLbl=1;backgroundOutline=1;size=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="200" y="690" width="320" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- infra_sqlite: x=880, y=690, w=320, h=100 → bbox x=880..1200, y=690..790. center_x=1040 -->
        <mxCell id="infra_sqlite" value="&lt;b&gt;SQLite + SQLCipher&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;端末ローカル DB&lt;br&gt;（Offline-First 一次記録）" style="shape=cylinder3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#FFFFFF;boundedLbl=1;backgroundOutline=1;size=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="880" y="690" width="320" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!--
          ARROWS
          Gap between FE layer bottom (y=220) and BE layer top (y=270) = y=220..270 (50px gap)
          Gap between BE layer bottom (y=430) and crate layer top (y=480) = y=430..480 (50px gap)
          Gap between crate layer bottom (y=620) and infra layer top (y=670) = y=620..670 (50px gap)
          Left margin: x=0..80 (80px)
          Right margin: x=1320..1400 (80px)
        -->

        <!-- FE-HA → terminal-api  (HTTPS :8080)
             fe_ha bottom center ≈ (230, 200), be_terminal top center ≈ (360, 300)
             Route: straight down through gap at x=230
             Segment: (230,200)→(230,300) — does not cross layer_be_label (x=96..376, y=278..302)?
               layer_be_label bbox: x=96, y=278, w=280, h=24 → x=96..376, y=278..302
               x=230 is inside [96,376], y segment 200→300 passes y=278..302 → crosses label (WARN transparent OK)
             Route slightly to x=500 (middle of be_terminal, outside label zone x=96..376):
             (360, 200)→(360, 300) — label x=96..376 y=278..302: x=360 inside → still crosses
             Use x=600 to avoid label entirely (label ends at x=376):
             Actually the label WARN is OK (transparent annotation). Only vertex/edge ERRORs block.
             Keep straight path. -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_ha_terminal" value="HTTPS :8080" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;" edge="1" parent="1" source="fe_ha" target="be_terminal">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="230" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="360" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="360" y="300" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-MA → master-api  (HTTPS :8081)
             fe_ma bottom center ≈ (700, 200), be_master top center ≈ (960, 300)
             Route: down at x=860 (center of be_master area) -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_ma_master" value="HTTPS :8081" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;" edge="1" parent="1" source="fe_ma" target="be_master">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="700" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="860" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="860" y="300" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-MC → master-api  (HTTPS :8081)
             fe_mc bottom center ≈ (1090, 200), be_master top area
             Route: down at x=1090, target x=1060 (right side of be_master) -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_mc_master" value="HTTPS :8081" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;" edge="1" parent="1" source="fe_mc" target="be_master">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="1090" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="1060" y="245" />
              <mxPoint x="1060" y="300" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- terminal-api → crate_domain (dependency)
             be_terminal bottom at ≈ (360, 410), crate_domain top at (185, 510)
             Route: down to y=455 (in gap), left to x=185, down to y=510
             Does x=185 at y=455..480 cross layer_crate_bg (y=480..620)? No, it enters at y=480.
             Actually at y=455 we're in the gap (y=430..480), safe. -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_terminal_domain" value="" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;" edge="1" parent="1" source="be_terminal" target="crate_domain">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="360" y="455" />
              <mxPoint x="185" y="455" />
              <mxPoint x="185" y="510" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- master-api → crate_domain (dependency)
             be_master bottom at ≈ (960, 410), crate_domain top at (185, 510)
             Route: down to y=455, left to x=185, down to y=510
             Path at y=455 from x=960 to x=185: does this cross be_terminal (x=110..610, y=300..410)?
             y=455 is below be_terminal (y ends at 410), safe.
             Does path cross crate_db (x=290..460, y=510..600)? At y=455 we're above crate layer, safe.
             -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_master_domain" value="" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;" edge="1" parent="1" source="be_master" target="crate_domain">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="960" y="455" />
              <mxPoint x="185" y="455" />
              <mxPoint x="185" y="510" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- terminal-api → PostgreSQL (app_event_insert)
             Route outside left edge of diagram: exit left side of be_terminal at (110, 355),
             go left to x=30, go down to y=740 (center of infra_pg), go right to x=200 (left edge of infra_pg).
             Segments:
               (110,355)→(30,355): outside layer (left of x=80), safe
               (30,355)→(30,740): left of x=80, safe (outside all layers)
               (30,740)→(200,740): y=740 is inside infra layer (y=670..810), x=30..200,
                 does it cross infra_pg? infra_pg x=200..520, y=690..790 → enters at x=200 which is edge. OK.
             Label "app_event_insert": placed along the vertical segment at x=30,
             label bbox ≈ at midpoint x=30, y≈(355+740)/2=547.5 — this is outside all vertices (at x=30). OK.
             -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_terminal_pg" value="app_event_insert" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;labelPosition=right;align=left;" edge="1" parent="1" source="be_terminal" target="infra_pg">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="30" y="355" />
              <mxPoint x="30" y="740" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- master-api → PostgreSQL (app_write)
             Route outside right edge: exit right side of be_master at (1210, 355),
             go right to x=1370, go down to y=820 (below infra_sqlite which ends at y=790),
             go left to x=360 (center of infra_pg), go up to y=790 (bottom of infra_pg).
             Segments:
               (1210,355)→(1370,355): right of be_master, inside page but outside all boxes
               (1370,355)→(1370,820): right margin (x=1370 > 1320=infra_bg right edge x=80+1240=1320)
               (1370,820)→(360,820): y=820 is below all infra boxes (infra_pg ends y=790, infra_sqlite ends y=790)
               (360,820)→(360,790): enters infra_pg from bottom
             Does (1370,355)→(1370,820) cross anything? x=1370 > layer_infra_bg right edge (x=80+1240=1320). Safe.
             Does (1370,820)→(360,820) cross infra_sqlite (x=880..1200, y=690..790)? y=820 > 790. Safe!
             Does it cross layer_infra_bg (x=80..1320, y=670..810)? y=820 > 810. Safe.
             Label "app_write" along right vertical, outside all boxes. -->
        <mxCell id="arrow_master_pg" value="app_write" style="endArrow=classic;endFill=1;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;edgeStyle=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;labelPosition=left;align=right;" edge="1" parent="1" source="be_master" target="infra_pg">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="1370" y="355" />
              <mxPoint x="1370" y="820" />
              <mxPoint x="360" y="820" />
              <mxPoint x="360" y="790" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-HA → SQLite (Offline-First)
             Route: exit bottom of fe_ha at (230, 200), go down to y=870 (below all layers),
             go right to x=1040 (center of infra_sqlite), go up to y=790 (bottom of infra_sqlite).
             Segments:
               (230,200)→(230,870): x=230 — does this cross anything?
                 fe_ha bottom at y=200: we start at (230,200) exit going down.
                 layer_fe_bg: y=60..220 → y=200..220: x=230 crosses layer_fe_bg bbox, but that's the source container — excluded by lint rule 4 ("source/target/their containers/bg are excluded").
                 Actually fe_ha is not a container of this edge; it's the source. Let me check if x=230 crosses any other vertex between y=200 and y=870:
                   layer_be_bg (x=80..1320, y=270..430): x=230 ∈ [80,1320], y=270..430 ∈ segment. CROSSES!
               Need to route around BE layer.
             Better route: exit fe_ha bottom at (110, 200) (left edge), go left to x=30, go down to y=870, go right to x=1040, go up to y=790.
             Segments:
               (110,200)→(30,200): inside layer_fe_bg (y=60..220), but source container — linter excludes source vertex's container? Actually layer_fe_bg is NOT the source (fe_ha is). So this segment might trigger a cross of layer_fe_bg.
               Hmm. Let me use the left outer margin approach but with the source waypoint starting just left of x=80 (outer edge).
             Cleanest: draw from fe_ha left edge (x=110, y=145) horizontally to x=28, then down to y=870, then right to x=1040, up to y=790.
             Segment (x=110..28, y=145): crosses layer_fe_bg (x=80..1320, y=60..220)? x=28 < 80 at this y, but the segment starts at x=110 inside layer. layer_fe_bg is NOT the source vertex but IS a vertex. ERROR.

             The linter excludes source vertex and its containers. But layer_fe_bg is neither fe_ha (source) nor its container (fe_ha parent=1, not layer_fe_bg). So we can't escape through layer_fe_bg.

             Actually I realize the most robust solution to avoid routing through all the layer background boxes is to not draw arrows through them. Instead I'll use a note/annotation at fe_ha that says "Offline-First → SQLite" rather than an actual edge. But the diagram is meant to show the architecture.

             Alternative: drop the FE-HA→SQLite arrow entirely and instead annotate fe_ha's label with "SQLite + SQLCipher" (which it already has). The infra_sqlite box is already in the diagram. The conceptual connection is clear from context. -->

        <!-- Note: FE-HA ↔ SQLite の直接接続は fe_ha のラベル内「SQLite + SQLCipher」で示す。
             ネットワーク経路ではなくローカル接続のため矢印は省略し、注釈テキストで補足する。 -->
        <mxCell id="note_ha_sqlite" value="※ FE-HA は SQLite に直接ローカル接続（Offline-First）" style="text;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="800" y="860" width="440" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- FE-HA → terminal-api で同期矢印を既に示しているので、
             SQLite はローカル DB として別途注釈のみで十分 -->

      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
